profile: Mezon Furniture is a Pointe-Claire, Montreal furniture store specializing in Canadian made household furniture, as well as upholstery, leather and custom furniture. Our goal is to offer an excellent quality product made for our clients needs. Mezon sells custom kitchen cabinets, bathroom vanities, entertainment wall units and home office systems as well as wooden furniture, predominantly made by Camlen Furniture.
